{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":660,"text":"I'm going to tell you about why I became a sculptor,"},{"time":4781,"text":"and you may think that sculptors,"},{"time":6836,"text":"well, they deal with meta, they deal with objects,"},{"time":12125,"text":"they deal with bodies,"},{"time":15083,"text":"but I think, really, what I care about most"},{"time":19626,"text":"is making space, and that's what I've called this talk:"},{"time":23674,"text":"Making Space."},{"time":26281,"text":"Space that exists within us,"},{"time":30689,"text":"and without us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32758,"text":"So, when I was a child,"},{"time":36927,"text":"I don't know how many of you grew up in the '50s,"},{"time":38938,"text":"but I was sent upstairs for an enforced rest. (Laughter)"},{"time":44350,"text":"It's a really bad idea. I mean, after lunch, you're, you know,"},{"time":47697,"text":"you're six, and you want to go and climb a tree."},{"time":50777,"text":"But I had to go upstairs, this tiny little room"},{"time":52666,"text":"that was actually made out of an old balcony,"},{"time":54441,"text":"so it was incredibly hot, small and light,"},{"time":59596,"text":"and I had to lie there. It was ridiculous."},{"time":63011,"text":"But anyway, for some reason, I promised myself"},{"time":65619,"text":"that I wasn't going to move,"},{"time":67872,"text":"that I was going to do this thing that Mummy"},{"time":69809,"text":"wanted me to do."},{"time":71736,"text":"And there I was, lying there in this tiny space,"},{"time":75409,"text":"hot, dark, claustrophobic, matchbox-sized, behind my eyes,"},{"time":81799,"text":"but it was really weird, like, after this went on"},{"time":85864,"text":"for days, weeks, months, that space would get bigger"},{"time":92577,"text":"and darker and cooler"},{"time":96241,"text":"until I really looked forward to that half an hour"},{"time":101111,"text":"of enforced immobility and rest,"},{"time":105218,"text":"and I really looked forward to going to that place"},{"time":109872,"text":"of darkness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112434,"text":"Do you mind if we do something completely different?"},{"time":114890,"text":"Can we all just close our eyes for a minute?"},{"time":116926,"text":"Now, this isn't going to be freaky."},{"time":118574,"text":"It isn't some cultic thing. (Laughter)"},{"time":120196,"text":"It's just, it's just, I just would like us all to go there."},{"time":123444,"text":"So I'm going to do it too. We'll all be there together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125592,"text":"So close your eyes for a minute."},{"time":129427,"text":"Here we are, in a space,"},{"time":132537,"text":"the subjective, collective space of the darkness of the body."},{"time":140009,"text":"I think of this as the place of imagination,"},{"time":144064,"text":"of potential,"},{"time":147364,"text":"but what are its qualities?"},{"time":150264,"text":"It is objectless. There are no things in it."},{"time":155561,"text":"It is dimensionless. It is limitless."},{"time":161512,"text":"It is endless."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166102,"text":"Okay, open your eyes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168648,"text":"That's the space that I think sculpture --"},{"time":172857,"text":"which is a bit of a paradox, sculpture that is about"},{"time":175925,"text":"making material propositions --"},{"time":179269,"text":"but I think that's the space"},{"time":181390,"text":"that sculpture can connect us with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186058,"text":"So, imagine we're in the middle of America."},{"time":190243,"text":"You're asleep. You wake up,"},{"time":193115,"text":"and without lifting your head from the earth"},{"time":196462,"text":"on your sleeping bag, you can see for 70 miles."},{"time":201900,"text":"This is a dry lake bed."},{"time":205151,"text":"I was young. I'd just finished art school."},{"time":209393,"text":"I wanted to do something that was working"},{"time":211565,"text":"directly with the world, directly with place."},{"time":216717,"text":"This was a wonderful place, because it was a place"},{"time":219780,"text":"where you could imagine that you were the"},{"time":221997,"text":"first person to be there."},{"time":224331,"text":"It was a place where nothing very much had happened."},{"time":229240,"text":"Anyway, bear with me."},{"time":232485,"text":"I picked up a hand-sized stone,"},{"time":236270,"text":"threw it as far as I was able,"},{"time":238363,"text":"it was about 22 meters."},{"time":240434,"text":"I then cleared all the stones within that radius"},{"time":246772,"text":"and made a pile."},{"time":250574,"text":"And that was the pile, by the way."},{"time":252978,"text":"And then, I stood on the pile,"},{"time":256475,"text":"and threw all of those rocks out again,"},{"time":260344,"text":"and here is rearranged desert."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265562,"text":"You could say, well, it doesn't look very different"},{"time":267540,"text":"from when he started."},{"time":269659,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":270862,"text":"What's all the fuss about?"},{"time":272496,"text":"In fact, Chris was worried and said,"},{"time":273864,"text":"\"Look, don't show them that slide,"},{"time":275258,"text":"because they're just going to think you're another one of"},{"time":277217,"text":"those crazy modern artists who doesn't do much."},{"time":279883,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":282253,"text":"But the fact is, this is evidence"},{"time":288962,"text":"of a living body on other bodies,"},{"time":292497,"text":"rocks that have been the subject of geological formation,"},{"time":298336,"text":"erosion, the action of time on objects."},{"time":303350,"text":"This is a place, in a way, that I just"},{"time":305872,"text":"would like you to, in a way, look at differently"},{"time":309353,"text":"because of this event that has happened in it,"},{"time":313024,"text":"a human event,"},{"time":315079,"text":"and in general, it just asks us to look again"},{"time":318631,"text":"at this world, so different from, in a way,"},{"time":321190,"text":"the world that we have been sharing with each other,"},{"time":324461,"text":"the technological world,"},{"time":326887,"text":"to look again at the elemental world."},{"time":331581,"text":"The elemental world that we all live in is that space"},{"time":337290,"text":"that we all visited together, the darkness of the body."},{"time":341678,"text":"I wanted to start again with that environment,"},{"time":345343,"text":"the environment of the intimate, subjective space"},{"time":349013,"text":"that each of us lives in, but from the other side"},{"time":352839,"text":"of appearance."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355447,"text":"So here is a daily activity of the studio."},{"time":357871,"text":"You can see I don't do much. I'm just standing there,"},{"time":361510,"text":"again with my eyes closed, and other people"},{"time":364237,"text":"are molding me, evidential."},{"time":368764,"text":"This is an indexical register of a lived moment"},{"time":372412,"text":"of a body in time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375595,"text":"Can we map that space, using the language of neutrinos"},{"time":381318,"text":"or cosmic rays, taking the bounding condition of the body"},{"time":386104,"text":"as its limit, but in complete reversal of, in a way,"},{"time":391579,"text":"the most traditional Greek idea of pointing?"},{"time":394202,"text":"In the old days they used to take a lump of Pentelic marble"},{"time":397990,"text":"and drill from the surface in order to identify the skin,"},{"time":402648,"text":"the appearance,"},{"time":404100,"text":"what Aristotle defined as the distinction"},{"time":407361,"text":"between substance and appearance,"},{"time":409384,"text":"the thing that makes things visible,"},{"time":412451,"text":"but here we're working from the other side."}]},{"cues":[{"time":415506,"text":"Or can we do it as an exclusive membrane?"},{"time":419551,"text":"This is a lead case made around the space"},{"time":425509,"text":"that my body occupied, but it's now void."},{"time":428974,"text":"This is a work called \"Learning To See.\""},{"time":432848,"text":"It's a bit of, well, we could call it night,"},{"time":439132,"text":"we could call it the 96 percent of gravity"},{"time":443582,"text":"that we don't know about, dark matter,"},{"time":447143,"text":"placed in space, anyway, another version of a human space"},{"time":450688,"text":"in space at large, but I don't know if you can see,"},{"time":453601,"text":"the eyes are indicated, they're closed."},{"time":459670,"text":"It's called \"Learning To See\" because it's about an object"},{"time":463133,"text":"that hopefully works reflexively and talks about that"},{"time":467465,"text":"vision or connection with the darkness of the body"},{"time":471284,"text":"that I see as a space of potential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":476257,"text":"Can we do it another way, using the language"},{"time":479332,"text":"of particles around a nucleus, and talk about the body"},{"time":482518,"text":"as an energy center?"},{"time":484448,"text":"No longer about statues, no longer having to take that"},{"time":487506,"text":"duty of standing, the standing of a human body,"},{"time":490567,"text":"or the standing of a statue, release it,"},{"time":493897,"text":"allow it to be an energy field, a space in space"},{"time":498155,"text":"that talks about human life, between becoming an entropy"},{"time":504976,"text":"as a sort of concentration of attention,"},{"time":509720,"text":"a human place of possibility in space at large."}]},{"cues":[{"time":514789,"text":"Is there another way?"},{"time":518565,"text":"Dark matter now placed against a horizon."},{"time":524664,"text":"If minds live in bodies, if bodies live in clothes,"},{"time":528699,"text":"and then in rooms, and then in buildings,"},{"time":531829,"text":"and then in cities, do they also have a final skin,"},{"time":537531,"text":"and is that skin perceptual?"},{"time":540164,"text":"The horizon."},{"time":542786,"text":"And is art about"},{"time":545287,"text":"trying to imagine what lies beyond the horizon?"},{"time":551231,"text":"Can we use, in a way, a body as an empty catalyst"},{"time":559852,"text":"for a kind of empathy with the experience"},{"time":564603,"text":"of space-time as it is lived, as I am standing here"},{"time":569951,"text":"in front of you trying to feel and make a connection"},{"time":575345,"text":"in this space-time that we are sharing,"},{"time":578651,"text":"can we use, at it were, the memory of a body,"},{"time":582207,"text":"of a human space in space to catalyze"},{"time":585031,"text":"an experience, again, firsthand experience,"},{"time":588754,"text":"of elemental time."},{"time":591761,"text":"Human time, industrial time, tested against"},{"time":596285,"text":"the time of the tides, in which these memories"},{"time":599281,"text":"of a particular body, that could be any body,"},{"time":604240,"text":"multiplied as in the time of mechanical reproduction,"},{"time":609130,"text":"many times, placed over three square miles,"},{"time":613515,"text":"a mile out to sea,"},{"time":617169,"text":"disappearing, in different conditions of day and night."},{"time":621524,"text":"You can see this work. It's on the mouth of the Mersey,"},{"time":624793,"text":"just outside Liverpool."},{"time":627950,"text":"And there you can see what a Liverpool sea looks like"},{"time":631415,"text":"on a typical afternoon."},{"time":634241,"text":"The pieces appear and disappear,"},{"time":636943,"text":"but maybe more importantly --"},{"time":639006,"text":"this is just looking north from the center of the installation --"},{"time":642939,"text":"they create a field, a field that involves"},{"time":647276,"text":"living and the surrogate bodies in a kind of relation,"},{"time":653038,"text":"a relation with each other and a relation with that limit,"},{"time":657999,"text":"the edge, the horizon."}]},{"cues":[{"time":661745,"text":"Just moving on, is it possible,"},{"time":664247,"text":"taking that idea of mind, body, body-building,"},{"time":668930,"text":"to supplant the first body,"},{"time":672335,"text":"the biological body, with the second,"},{"time":674315,"text":"the body of architecture and the built environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":677233,"text":"This is a work called \"Room for the Great Australian Desert.\""},{"time":681824,"text":"It's in an undefined location"},{"time":683442,"text":"and I've never published where it is."},{"time":686523,"text":"It's an object for the mind."},{"time":688413,"text":"I think of it as a 21st-century Buddha."},{"time":691834,"text":"Again, the darkness of the body,"},{"time":693764,"text":"now held within this bunker shape"},{"time":696827,"text":"of the minimum position that a body needs to occupy,"},{"time":700311,"text":"a crouching body."},{"time":702427,"text":"There's a hole at the anus, penis level."},{"time":705414,"text":"There are holes at ears. There are no holes at the eyes."},{"time":708151,"text":"There's a slot for the mouth. It's two and a half inches thick,"},{"time":712405,"text":"concrete with a void interior."},{"time":714744,"text":"Again, a site found with a completely flat"},{"time":718927,"text":"360-degree horizon."},{"time":723623,"text":"This is just simply asking, again,"},{"time":727947,"text":"as if we had arrived for the first time,"},{"time":732535,"text":"what is the relationship of the human project"},{"time":736671,"text":"to time and space?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":740784,"text":"Taking that idiom of, as it were,"},{"time":744357,"text":"the darkness of the body transferred to architecture,"},{"time":749350,"text":"can you use architectural space not for living"},{"time":752925,"text":"but as a metaphor,"},{"time":754638,"text":"and use its systolic, diastolic"},{"time":758415,"text":"smaller and larger spaces to provide a kind of"},{"time":763234,"text":"firsthand somatic narrative for a journey through space,"},{"time":768906,"text":"light and darkness?"},{"time":772202,"text":"This is a work of some proportion and some weight"},{"time":777724,"text":"that makes the body into a city, an aggregation of cells"},{"time":782610,"text":"that are all interconnected"},{"time":785022,"text":"and that allow certain visual access"},{"time":789854,"text":"at certain places."}]},{"cues":[{"time":792653,"text":"The last work that I just wanted to share with you"},{"time":799356,"text":"is \"Blind Light,\" which is perhaps"},{"time":803158,"text":"the most open work,"},{"time":806418,"text":"and in a conference of radical openness,"},{"time":808553,"text":"I think maybe this is as radical as I get,"},{"time":812561,"text":"using light and water vapor as my materials."},{"time":816824,"text":"Here is a box"},{"time":819210,"text":"filled at one and a half atmospheres of atmospheric pressure,"},{"time":822752,"text":"with a cloud and with very bright light."},{"time":826791,"text":"As you walk towards the ever-open threshold,"},{"time":830212,"text":"you disappear, both to yourselves and to others."},{"time":838124,"text":"If you hold your hand out in front of you,"},{"time":840280,"text":"you can't see it."},{"time":842134,"text":"If you look down, you can't see your feet."},{"time":845400,"text":"You are now consciousness without an object,"},{"time":852402,"text":"freed from the dimensionful"},{"time":856295,"text":"and measured way in which life links us"},{"time":862181,"text":"to the obligatory."},{"time":865271,"text":"But this is a space that is actually filled with people,"},{"time":870248,"text":"disembodied voices,"},{"time":872218,"text":"and out of that ambient environment,"},{"time":876332,"text":"when people come close to your own body zone,"},{"time":880262,"text":"very close, they appear to you as representations."},{"time":884325,"text":"When they appear close to the edge,"},{"time":886545,"text":"they are representations, representations in which"},{"time":891129,"text":"the viewers have become the viewed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":894997,"text":"For me, art is not about objects of high monetary exchange."},{"time":900848,"text":"It's about reasserting our firsthand experience"},{"time":906253,"text":"in present time."},{"time":909144,"text":"As John Cage said,"},{"time":912585,"text":"\"We are not moving towards some kind of goal."},{"time":917672,"text":"We are at the goal, and it is changing with us."},{"time":922353,"text":"If art has any purpose, it is to open our eyes to that fact.\""},{"time":928789,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":930826,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}